                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8623" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0139</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2786 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">DR集团的国际布局新篇章——走好海外项目公司选址关键步</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A new chapter in the international layout of DR Group-take the key step in the site selection of overseas project companies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田波，王拓，刘昌辉，葛安康，何乐天</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迪瑞医疗科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海外项目公司布局；选址；SWOT分析法；层次分析法；模糊综合评价法；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Overseas project company layout; site selection; SWOT; AHP; fuzzy comprehensive evaluation method</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">选址是概念阶段的关键步骤，是可行性研究中必不可少的环节。它直接影响项目的定位、成本及周期等方面。本案例从项目内临时业务组组长小金的视角出发，描述了DR集团在决定进行海外项目公司建设之后，对10个选址地国家进行信息收集和分析、布局模式选择和初批选址地评价决策的过程。DR集团响应“一带一路”号召，进军海外，向IVD头部企业迈进。在建设地确定过程中，项目组经历了抉择困难、布局分歧和相关影响因素难以量化等问题。小金带领项目组成员对各选址地的政治、经济、技术等因素进行了权重分配和分数计算，成功将定性特点转化为定量数据，帮助DR集团完成了初批建设地的确定，走好了海外布局的坚实第一步。通过本案例的思考和学习，学生可以更好地掌握企业国际化动因理论、偏好决策理论等相关知识，了解项目公司选址的影响因素，更好地使用SWOT 分析、层次分析法、模糊综合评价法等评价决策方法，并掌握各种评价决策方法在选址排序等实践中的应用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Site selection is a critical step in the conceptual stage and an essential component of feasibility studies. It directly impacts the project positioning, cost and timeline. From the perspective of the project leader Jin, this case describes the process of information collection and analysis, the selection of layout patterns, and the initial evaluations for 10 potential site countries after deciding to establish overseas project companies. In response to &quot;the Belt and Road&quot; initiative, DR Group ventures into overseas expansion. During the site determination process, the project team encountered challenges in decision-making difficulties, layout disagreements, and quantifying related influencing factors. Jin leads the team members to carry out weight allocation and score calculation for political, economic, technical and other factors of each site selection, which helps DR Group finalizes their initial construction sites as a solid first step in their overseas expansion strategy. Through the analysis and study of this case, students can better grasp the theory of enterprise internationalization motivation, decision preference and other relevant knowledge, understand the influencing factors of site selection, better use analysis, AHP, and other methods, and master the application of various evaluation methods in site selection and other practices.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》、《工程项目管理》、《项目管理应用》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目管理阶段划分；影响选址的因素；SWOT分析；AHP（层次分析法）；模糊综合评价法；决策偏好理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
